{"word":"ἐνεργάζομαι","slug":"ἐνεργάζομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐνεργάζομαι</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>σομαι</el>) </el><p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a> <i>to make</i> or <i>produce in</i>, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:dative'>dat.</a>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>:—aor1 <el>ἐνειργάσθην</el> in <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>pass.</a></a> sense, <i>to be placed in</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to work for hire in</i> a place, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>; <el>ἐνεργ. τῇ οὐσίᾳ</el> <i>to trade</i> with the property, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}